name: CAIDA WHOIS Dumps
description:
CAIDA's WHOIS dumps archive, a general outline of files in this dataset can be found below:
  (date).(RIR name).db.gz is a dump of the named RIR's whois dump
  (date).delegated-(RIR name).txt.gz is the RIR delegation files
  (date).delegated-(RIR name)-extended.txt.gz is the RIR extended delegation files
  (date).iana.as-numbers.(txt/xml).gz is IANA's autonomous system number allocations to RIRs
  (date).iana.(ipv4/ipv6)-address-space.(txt/xml).gz is the ipv4/ipv6 address space registry
  (date).potaroo.autnum.txt.gz is a list of AS numbers and names
